{"tid":1402773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「行快啲行快啲」「快啲走快啲走」 走撚完未啊？","createTime":"2019-08-03T16:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:00:12.000Z","uid":7971,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db7e33ef5e8538192c1bc58273ead2628777e6ee","tid":1402773,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:56:23.000Z","msg":"真係好撚燥 次次打親LOL隻online game<br />\n仲係有啲人 [特別係女]<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一見到對家開幾槍TG <br />\n就大叫快啲走快啲走<br />\n再叫句行快啲 行快啲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n上個禮拜已經係咁 都算<br />\n今個星期 見親個個裝備upgrade哂<br />\n又粉紅嘴 又鐳射眼 <br />\n啊 我屌<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成大半條街 都可以有人大叫走快啲 <br />\n之後就成班雞飛狗走<br />\n係未想 人踩人啊 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n對唔住 <br />\n係現場隻game 真係即時忍唔住開聲屌<br />\n叫大家慢慢走<br />\n我依家都想屌多次<br />\n唔該 走 散水 be water  大家明<br />\n但有成大段距離 對家只係TG<br />\n你又full 裝 要唔要驚成咁<br />\n咁你買裝做咩 用黎打卡啊？<br />\n係未要前場真空 張前面當condom？<br />\n係未要人踩人？<br />\n點解中間偏前個班唔可以慢慢行？<br />\n係要叫人跑？<br />\n<br />\n大家都驚 都淆 <br />\n但唔係一有事 就叫人快跑 <br />\n更何況 你成個粉紅嘴最靚裝<br />\n根本唯恐天下不亂！"},{"pid":"66d787e463b97e4ac424c9cd5ee81fa710e06798","tid":1402773,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"已經見過2次"},{"pid":"ad811f733774d7501b0dda8fe42ab0250ffc6ecb","tid":1402773,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:57:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd9c57f8257c779a8b6e235014542fd30e4dd1a8","tid":1402773,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4f476534eab0dcfa2ab23db5535c762fd7f3ac","tid":1402773,"uid":93998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:00:12.000Z","msg":"最好就拉撚晒班示威者 搞亂香港<br /